    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! This beauty has been totally babied\u2014not a scratch or a dent in sight, and the interior still feels brand new. It\u2019s been kept in a garage and runs like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s in flawless shape without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
